title: Prime Minister welcomes the Head of the Government of Libyan National Unity
text: The Prime Minister, Mr Abdelaziz DJERAD, welcomed, this Saturday, May 29, 2021 at the international airport of Algiers Houari Boumediene, the Head of the Government of Libyan National Unity, Mr Abdelhamid DBEIBAH, who is undertaking on May 29 and 30, an official visit to Algeria at the head of an important ministerial delegation.
The Prime Minister was accompanied by the Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri BOUKADOUM, and the Minister of Trade, Mr Kamel REZIG.
